<section class="how-it-works" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="how-it-works-title">
  <h2 id="how-it-works-title">How it works</h2>

  <ol class="how-steps">
    <li>
      <span class="step-label">Sign in</span> with your AT Protocol handle. Bluesky, Blacksky, North Sky, or your own PDS. No new account, no phone number.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="step-label">Build your buddy list</span> and organize people into trust tiers. See who's online, set your status.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="step-label">Call anyone</span> with one click. Free, encrypted, cross-platform. Send IMs when you can't hop on video. For offline DMs, we link out to Germ.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p class="how-footer">
    Your identity, contacts, and public chat history are yours. Portable across any app that implements the Lexicon.
  </p>
</section>
